QuestData.Title: Attack At The Temple of the Jade Serpent
QuestData.Description: Darkness enshrouds the Temple of the Jade Serpent, and Yu'Lon's priests beseech us for aid.$B$BThey hold the sha in check, but just barely.$B$BYou may be able to turn the tide, $c.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Elder Sage Tai-Feng at the Jade Temple Grounds in The Jade Forest.
